Created:
- `/src/components/error-boundary.tsx`

Modified:
- `/src/app/api/predict/route.ts`
- `/src/app/predict/predict-page-client.tsx`
- `/src/components/predict/prediction-result.tsx`
- `/src/components/predict/tweet-input.tsx`

All lint and typecheck tests passed.
